## Add ObservedChat Schema and Transport Interface Method

The chatId picker in the BindingDialog needs live data from observed chats. This task adds the schema and transport interface method.

### Schema

In `packages/shared/src/relay-adapter-schemas.ts`, add after the existing binding schemas:

```typescript
export const ObservedChatSchema = z.object({
  chatId: z.string(),
  displayName: z.string().optional(),
  channelType: ChannelTypeSchema.optional(),
  lastMessageAt: z.string().datetime(),
  messageCount: z.number(),
});

export type ObservedChat = z.infer<typeof ObservedChatSchema>;

